==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Maverick brand
<hw>Maverick brand</hw>. <def>A brand originated by a dishonest
cattleman, who, without owning any stock, gradually accumulates a herd
by finding mavericks.</def> <mark>[Western U. S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mavis</ent>⟦br⟧
